ABILITIES

Usage: ^gABILITIES^n

If you are an adept, over time you will gain various abilities that represent
certain levels of mastery you've achieved with your body. This command will
display any abilities you have learned, along with their level where applicable.

The number in yellow displays how many ranks of that power you currently have
activated.

^WSee Also: ADEPTS, POWER POINTS, ACTIVATE^n
